{"type":"article","id":13198,"title":"时评作家王亚军因发布武汉肺炎负面消息，被湖北有司威胁后“封口”","uid":12696,"topics":[375,5262],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/20REqN9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/20REqN9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/20REqN9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xA09wK2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xA09wK2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xA09wK2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Za7WX9B.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Za7WX9B.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Za7WX9B.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n时评人王亚军比较早地关注到了武汉的疫情，因此在一月上、中旬连发了好几篇疫情相关的负面文章，后来当他开始通过自己的人脉联系厂家为武汉筹措医用物资时（1月24号），先是微信号被封，后来又接到湖北有关部门的威胁电话，要求他闭嘴不然关看守所。于是在昨天，王亚军在推特上和油管上删光了自己的疫情相关推文和视频，主动“封口”。<br>\n<br>\n他的自述视频地址:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenqiushi404/status/1221267788297191424\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">链接</a>","date":"2020-01-28","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}